By: Zhuangzi
Locus:
  Chapter: 17
  Paragraph: 50
Title: Autumn Floods
---
Chuang Tzu and Hui Tzu were strolling along the dam of the Hao River
when Chuang Tzu said, "See how the minnows come out and dart around
where they please! That's what fish really enjoy!"
